{"tid":995044,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jennie、Kai分手了　「戀情見光死」好友證實：為了粉絲分開","createTime":"2019-01-25T07:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T01:22:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":98,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"2527e39208841d511c434a290598955cc33af220","tid":995044,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣偶像團體EXO Kai於2019年元旦當天遭抓包約會Jennie，怎料，兩人才剛認愛1個月不到，25日傳出分手消息，韓媒《sbsfune》獨家報導，兩人已經分手了，現在各自集中彼此的事業中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3803/d3803842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3803%2Fd3803842.jpg&h=1e4c07ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲好友爆料，KAI和Jennie分手了。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n根據韓媒報導，Kai身邊友人向媒體爆料，「Kai跟Jennie最近退回樂壇的前後輩關係了，因為還有很多事要做，因此決定分開。」兩人都認為事業比愛情重要，未來將會集中在自己的事業上，據雙方友人表示，兩人是為了粉絲而分手。<br />\n<br />\nEXO Kai與Jennie元旦當天被爆出約會照，震驚大批粉絲，戀愛曝光後，粉絲開始尋找蛛絲馬跡，才發現原來他們10月就已在IG曬愛，分別貼出「情侶視角」約會照，間接坐實戀情。爾後，SM也出面證實「彼此抱有好感」，怎料，這段戀情不到1個月見光死，兩人最後決定繼續打拼事業，退回前後輩的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760a95fb64de147ea644755a2f93dc445de72282","tid":995044,"uid":74065,"like":313,"dislike":9,"score":304,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"JENNIE始終係老楊既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d559e7bc80d8860fb3ec5ddf71f09b97f4d497cd","tid":995044,"uid":555,"like":32,"dislike":63,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦傻kai"},{"pid":"45f144f6dbd6ea5c1e4c577a01f162a752b805c4","tid":995044,"uid":18196,"like":65,"dislike":6,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"中出即飛了"},{"pid":"a4896ea47e4a7948e917da1a9a39e80e1a56af79","tid":995044,"uid":223790,"like":134,"dislike":27,"score"